    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras/8fddc02ca6a31a66db1ce3a8d5daacb6.poster.avif?t=1767173659\" width=1170 height=367 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras/8fddc02ca6a31a66db1ce3a8d5daacb6.webm?t=1767173659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras/f1dbfb71c839ae0f5fd40d3d728777b6.avif?t=1767173659\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras_big/f1dbfb71c839ae0f5fd40d3d728777b6.webp?t=1767173659 width=1560 height=98 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>恭喜您，已被录用进入试用期！</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Blueman 公司需要有动力的实习生，愿意承担各种工作：整理工位、喂恶魔、督促他人工作，并且不多问就参与公司团建游戏。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras/4246de28eac6df53b4f315b1dbdbba9a.poster.avif?t=1767173659\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3135260/extras/4246de28eac6df53b4f315b1dbdbba9a.webm?t=1767173659\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在试用期内，您将一路向上逐层前进：每一层都有一项新的「重要任务」，不知为何偏偏交给您。完成所有考验——谁知道呢，也许有一天，下达命令的人就会变成您。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>万金油实习生。</strong>玩家扮演那个什么都往身上堆的人：从「小差事」到关系到整个部门命运的任务。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>没有枯燥的流水线。</strong>每一关都是一款自带规则的小型游戏。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不容出错的试用期。</strong>失误会重置当前关卡，细节把控成为玩法核心。这营造出真实的试用期感受：对您要求近乎完美，却几乎不把话说明白。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>和工作可疑地相像的地狱。</strong>阴暗与恶魔背后，是熟悉的办公室现实。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>短小却饱满的体验。</strong>紧凑的体量让您能在一次游玩中走完实习生的全部旅程——从第一项任务到最后一层。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>预计完成时间：约 60 分钟</strong></p>",
